              <p class="c-article-rights"><a data-track="click" data-track-action="view rights and permissions" data-track-label="link" href="https://s100.copyright.com/AppDispatchServlet?title=Toward%20transparent%20and%20accurate%20housing%20price%20appraisal%3A%20Hedonic%20price%20models%20versus%20machine%20learning%20algorithms&amp;author=Sihyun%20An%20et%20al&amp;contentID=10.1186%2Fs40854-025-00874-w&amp;copyright=The%20Author%28s%29&amp;publication=2199-4730&amp;publicationDate=2025-12-31&amp;publisherName=SpringerNature&amp;orderBeanReset=true&amp;oa=CC%20BY">Reprints and permissions</a></p></div></div></section><section aria-labelledby="article-info" data-title="About this article"><div class="c-article-section" id="article-info-section"><h2 class="c-article-section__title js-section-title js-c-reading-companion-sections-item" id="article-info">About this article</h2><div class="c-article-section__content" id="article-info-content"><div class="c-bibliographic-information"><div class="u-hide-print c-bibliographic-information__column c-bibliographic-information__column--border"><a data-crossmark="10.1186/s40854-025-00874-w" target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://crossmark.crossref.org/dialog/?doi=10.1186/s40854-025-00874-w" data-track="click" data-track-action="Click Crossmark" data-track-label="link" data-test="crossmark"><img loading="lazy" width="57" height="81" alt="Check for updates. Verify currency and authenticity via CrossMark" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,"></a></div><div class="c-bibliographic-information__column"><h3 class="c-article__sub-heading" id="citeas">Cite this article</h3><p class="c-bibliographic-information__citation">An, S., Song, Y., Jang, H. <i>et al.</i> Toward transparent and accurate housing price appraisal: Hedonic price models versus machine learning algorithms.
